txt.en: For those visiting the Beorninghús, it is important to help in the daily work of Beornings.
Eggs can be found at the Beorninghús.\n\nYou should collect some eggs for Gírta.
Gírta can be found at the Beorninghús.\n\nYou should bring the eggs to Gírta.
Gírta has asked you to gather some eggs from chicken nests around the Beorninghús. The chickens do not seem to mind!

'This is truly a good collection of eggs from our wonderful chickens. I will put these eggs to good use, and I know they will be appreciated by all who sit at my table. I know more than one dozen ways of preparing eggs for supper, each of them different, and each of them delicious. I believe no one in all the vales knows more about the preparation and enjoyment of eggs than I do!'
